      *
     C                     MOVE BBSHN1    K@SHN1
     C                     MOVE BBSHN2    K@SHN2
     C                     MOVE BBSHN3    K@SHN3
     C           K#FCE     CHAINFCEPL01              92
     C           *IN92     IFEQ *ON
      * IAF PART#
