     C                     PARM           PTOKU   4
     C                     PARM           PNONY   4
     C                     PARM           PNKOJ   1
     C                     PARM           PNUKE   4
     C                     PARM           PMHIN  20
     C                     PARM           PSHIN  12
     C                     PARM           PFLAG   1
